00:05:29.496 --> 00:05:31.498 position:50% align:center
and the only thing part-time
about her job as my maid

00:05:31.581 --> 00:05:33.958 position:50% align:center
was the small part of her
childhood when she wasn't!

00:05:34.042 --> 00:05:35.251 position:50% align:center
Stop eating her lies up

00:05:35.335 --> 00:05:37.462 position:50% align:center
like they're
your favorite flavor!

00:05:37.545 --> 00:05:39.589 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA]
So basically,

00:05:39.673 --> 00:05:42.425 position:50% align:center
I've used my parents' computer
for as long as I can remember.

00:05:42.509 --> 00:05:45.136 position:50% align:center
But I saved up my money
and now I want my own!

00:05:45.220 --> 00:05:46.304 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Ah.

00:05:46.388 --> 00:05:47.639 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] It's only
a matter of time before

00:05:47.722 --> 00:05:49.766 position:50% align:center
the president catches
her in one of these lies.

00:05:49.849 --> 00:05:51.726 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] He's sharp
about things like that.

00:05:51.810 --> 00:05:53.061 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] Working to
pay for what she wants

00:05:53.144 --> 00:05:55.313 position:50% align:center
instead of relying on
her parents. That's great!

00:05:55.397 --> 00:05:57.357 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
He's been duped!

00:05:57.440 --> 00:05:59.484 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] What do you plan
on using the computer for?

00:05:59.567 --> 00:06:00.902 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA]
Hmm.

00:06:00.985 --> 00:06:03.196 position:50% align:center
Mostly research and putting
school reports together.

00:06:03.279 --> 00:06:05.073 position:50% align:center
Oh! And videos!

00:06:05.156 --> 00:06:07.075 position:50% align:center
Especially if
they're of cute cats!

00:06:07.158 --> 00:06:09.119 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
It's all lies! C'mon, President.

00:06:09.202 --> 00:06:11.496 position:50% align:center
Surely you won't fall
for such an obvious trap.

00:06:11.579 --> 00:06:13.039 position:50% align:center
She would rather watch
things get crushed

00:06:13.123 --> 00:06:15.959 position:50% align:center
in a machine press than
a cute cat curled up on a rug!

00:06:16.042 --> 00:06:17.168 position:50% align:center
[CAT meows]

00:06:17.252 --> 00:06:20.005 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Cats! Yeah! I get it.

00:06:20.088 --> 00:06:23.842 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
You're killing me here!

00:06:23.925 --> 00:06:27.512 position:50% align:center
You can watch videos on anything
so you should be covered.

00:06:27.595 --> 00:06:30.432 position:50% align:center
Good to know!
I'll choose by design, then!

00:06:30.515 --> 00:06:31.975 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA] This is coming
from the girl who installs

00:06:32.058 --> 00:06:34.477 position:50% align:center
