her computer herself!

00:06:34.561 --> 00:06:36.896 position:50% align:center
It'll be over once she
makes her "final selection,"

00:06:36.980 --> 00:06:38.732 position:50% align:center
then we can finally
close the chapter

00:06:38.815 --> 00:06:40.692 position:50% align:center
on this little
misadventure. [giggles]

00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:42.068 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
So in other words,

00:06:42.152 --> 00:06:44.362 position:50% align:center
solving it with the
probability recurrence formula,

00:06:44.446 --> 00:06:47.073 position:50% align:center
which derives case analyses, is
more efficient in the long run.

00:06:47.157 --> 00:06:48.700 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
When did he start tutoring her?

00:06:48.783 --> 00:06:51.786 position:50% align:center
He's never offered
to help me study before!

00:06:51.870 --> 00:06:54.372 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] There's really not all
that much I can teach you.

00:06:54.456 --> 00:06:56.624 position:50% align:center
Isn't Firis Academy a top
school, too?

00:06:56.708 --> 00:06:59.878 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA] It is, but I'm not
the best at taking tests.

00:06:59.961 --> 00:07:05.008 position:50% align:center
[sighs] Stinks. Even though
I study ten hours a day.

00:07:05.091 --> 00:07:05.884 position:50% align:center
[yawns]

00:07:05.967 --> 00:07:07.177 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
Ten hours?

00:07:07.260 --> 00:07:09.387 position:50% align:center
So we're walking down
the same thorny path!

00:07:09.471 --> 00:07:11.681 position:50% align:center
