for three hours?

00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:39.084 position:50% align:center
I tried to wake
you up a few times.

00:07:39.167 --> 00:07:42.045 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA]
Oh, my gosh. How embarrassing!

00:07:42.128 --> 00:07:43.838 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA whines]

00:07:43.922 --> 00:07:45.507 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
You think you're so sly,

00:07:45.590 --> 00:07:47.425 position:50% align:center
but I caught you stealing
glances at the president

00:07:47.509 --> 00:07:50.470 position:50% align:center
