keep you this long.

00:07:53.682 --> 00:07:56.309 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI] And leave a defenseless
girl all by herself?

00:07:56.393 --> 00:07:57.435 position:50% align:center
Not happening.

00:07:57.519 --> 00:07:58.645 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:07:58.728 --> 00:08:01.564 position:50% align:center
