is a sign of effort.

00:08:01.648 --> 00:08:03.024 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA]
Shirogane.

00:08:03.108 --> 00:08:05.193 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] She's giving
Shirogane the look.

00:08:05.276 --> 00:08:06.361 position:50% align:center
