Hayaska has mastered the art.

00:08:14.494 --> 00:08:16.454 position:50% align:center
She's a pro!

00:08:16.538 --> 00:08:18.873 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA]
Say, Shirogane.

00:08:18.957 --> 00:08:21.334 position:50% align:center
Would you wanna go
out with me sometime?

00:08:21.418 --> 00:08:22.627 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
Damn.

00:08:22.711 --> 00:08:25.588 position:50% align:center
What man could turn
down an invite like that?

00:08:25.672 --> 00:08:27.007 position:50% align:center
We could take a modern approach

00:08:27.090 --> 00:08:29.342 position:50% align:center
and I'll be 90 percent friend,
ten percent girlfriend,

00:08:29.426 --> 00:08:32.137 position:50% align:center
