better acquainted.

00:08:32.220 --> 00:08:33.680 position:50% align:center
Even if there's
another girl you like,

00:08:33.763 --> 00:08:35.432 position:50% align:center
that doesn't bother me at all!

00:08:35.515 --> 00:08:37.559 position:50% align:center
You can still be with her and
I'll just be your side piece!

00:08:37.642 --> 00:08:39.602 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR] Conceptual ambiguity!

00:08:39.686 --> 00:08:41.146 position:50% align:center
Not only is this girl cute,

00:08:41.229 --> 00:08:43.356 position:50% align:center
but she's willing to be a lil'
somethin' somethin' on the side

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:47.027 position:50% align:center
while he figures out what he
really wants in a girlfriend.

00:08:47.110 --> 00:08:48.778 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
I was wrong.

00:08:48.862 --> 00:08:50.655 position:50% align:center
