made you do this!

00:08:50.739 --> 00:08:51.990 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
I'm sorry.

00:08:52.073 --> 00:08:54.075 position:50% align:center
But... there's
another girl I like.

00:08:54.159 --> 00:08:55.577 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA gasps]

00:08:58.747 --> 00:09:01.791 position:50% align:center
Ah... I see.

00:09:01.875 --> 00:09:04.878 position:50% align:center
She's one lucky girl.

00:09:04.961 --> 00:09:08.548 position:50% align:center
Hope everything works out
for the both of you, truly.

