00:09:16.765 --> 00:09:18.683 position:50% align:center
He's definitely
a tough nut to crack.

00:09:18.767 --> 00:09:20.018 position:50% align:center
--And you thought it'd be easy.

00:09:20.101 --> 00:09:20.977 position:50% align:center
