--And you thought it'd be easy.

00:09:21.061 --> 00:09:22.103 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA gasps]

00:09:22.187 --> 00:09:23.355 position:50% align:center
And besides,

00:09:23.438 --> 00:09:26.191 position:50% align:center
I never said that it
would only take one day!

00:09:26.274 --> 00:09:27.025 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Uh...

00:09:27.108 --> 00:09:28.693 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA growls]

00:09:28.777 --> 00:09:30.945 position:50% align:center
Give me a month and
he'll be head over heels!

00:09:31.029 --> 00:09:32.989 position:50% align:center
A day just made
me look desperate!

00:09:33.073 --> 00:09:34.824 position:50% align:center
I didn't wanna do it to begin
with!

00:09:34.908 --> 00:09:36.117 position:50% align:center
[KAGUYA]
Uh...

00:09:36.201 --> 00:09:37.285 position:50% align:center
[HAYASAKA] The only
reason I went through this

00:09:37.369 --> 00:09:38.870 position:50% align:center
